snippet.title: Crossy Road Castle Console - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Shoot out of cannons, ride rainbows, and make your way through a maze of never-ending levels in Crossy Road Castle! Bring your friends into the fray with co-op mode for even more chaotic fun. The award-winning Apple Arcade hit is landing on Nintendo Switch™, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X|S on the following dates:

Melbourne, Australia - September 12, 1:00am AEST
Tokyo, Japan - September 12, 00:00am JST
Berlin, Germany - September 11, 5:00pm CEST
Los Angeles, USA - September 11, 8:00am PDT
